# Specs

## Purpose

This directory contains generated machine-readable contracts for `${loop_dir_name}`.

## Contents

- `objective/`: generated objective and success-posture contracts when used.
- `collab/`: generated process, topology, scheduling, and collaboration contracts.
- `comms/`: generated message schemas, template registry, and renderers when communication is structured.
- `state/`: generated bookkeeping state contracts when runtime state is needed.
- `workspace/`: generated workspace contracts when agents need work roots or shared resources.
- `run/`: generated run artifact contracts when execution preserves durable artifacts.
- `participants/`: generated participant role and instance contracts.
